     <h2>
      <a href="/">
       mnmlst
      </a>
      :
      <b>
       sng nttnl vlcty
      </b>
     </h2>
     <div class="entry">
      <p>
       Ths dys I s th smpl Mc prgrm
       <a href="http://notational.net/">
        Nttnl Vlcty
       </a>
       t wrt nrly vrythng — nts, lsts, tds, ds, blg psts, bk chptrs, rmblng rnts t th gvrnmnt, nd s n.
      </p>
      <p>
       I ntd ths n  ftr Shwn Blnc dd n
       <a href="http://shawnblanc.net/2010/08/leo-babauta-mac-setup/">
        my Swt Mc Stp
       </a>
       (nd ndd t s swt), nd svrl rdrs skd fr n lbrtn – hw d I s NV?
      </p>
      <p>
       It’s nt cmplctd. Nttnl, s mny f y mght knw, s  lghtwght prgrm tht ds smthng vry smpl:
      </p>
      <ul>
       <li>
        It llws y t wrt txt.
       </li>
       <li>
        It svs ths txts tmtclly — y nvr hv t prss Sv.
       </li>
       <li>
        It lts y fnd ths txts vry sly thrgh  srch br tht dsplys mtchs s y typ th srch, vry smlr t Ggl Instnt.
       </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
       Th lst prt s th mgc. In th lctn br, y jst strt typng, nd nstntly whtvr y’r lkng fr pprs. Als f y strt typng  nm f  nw fl y wnt t crt, y jst prss Rtrn nd th nw fl s crt — n nd t g t “Nw Fl” r smthng lk tht n  mn.
      </p>
      <span id="more-634">
      </span>
      <br/>
      And by lrnng n kybrd shrtct — Cmd-L t nstntly g t th “lctn br” — y nvr nd t s th ms. Jst typ Cmd-L, strt typng yr srch r nw fl nm, nd prss Rtrn whn y’r dn. Thn strt typng r dtng wth th kybrd.
      <p>
       It’s xtrmly smpl, bt t wrks bttr thn ny thr txt dtr I’v sd, nd s I dcdd t wld b ll I s. I hvn’t lkd bck.
      </p>
      <h3>
       My Stp
      </h3>
      I’v st p  cpl thngs wrth ntng:
      <br/>
      <ol>
       <li>
        Undr Prfrncs/Nts/Strg, I’v st t t str nts s pln txt fls. Ths llws m t ml ndvdl txt fls t ppl f ncssry, t pn thm n thr txt dtrs, nd t ccss th fls frm my phn f ndd.
       </li>
       <li>
        I ls hv t synchrnzng wth
        <a href="http://simplenoteapp.com/">
         Smplnt’s
        </a>
        nln srvc. I dn’t s Smplnt s I dn’t hv n Phn (f I dd I wld) bt I lk hvng ll my nts bckd p nd ccssbl nln. Y cn d ths ndr Prfrncs/Nts/Synchrnztn. It’s fr.
       </li>
       <li>
        Lstly, I mvd th “Nttnl Dt” fldr n whch ll th pln txt nts r strd t my
        <a href="http://www.dropbox.com/">
         Drpbx
        </a>
        fldr. I hvn’t sd ths yt, s I nly s n cmptr yt nd dn’t nd t ccss my fls frm thr cmptrs, bt I lk tht t’s nstntly bckd p nd ccssbl nln — nc gn. It’s ls fr nd sy t st p.
       </li>
      </ol>
      <h3>
       My Usg
      </h3>
      Wht s thr t sy bt sg? I dn’t d t mch nsl, bt hr r  fw nts:
      <br/>
      <ol>
       <li>
        I ppnd prfxs t th fl nms s I cn grp thngs — s fr Zn Hbts psts, I’ll hv  “zh-” prfx, bfr th pst tpc, s tht whn I strt typng “zh” t’ll shw ll my Zn Hbts drfts. I d th sm fr mnmlst psts, chptrs nd nts fr my nw bk “fcs”, nd ntrvws.
       </li>
       <li>
        I mk th txt dtng fld  bt bggr thn dflt. I jst lk mr spc. Othr thn tht, vrythng s dflt, ncldng fnt nd txt sz nd ll tht.
       </li>
       <li>
        It wld b nc f y cld wrt n fll-scrn md n
        <span class="caps">
         NV,
        </span>
        bt nstd I wll jst pst  fl nt
        <a href="http://www.hogbaysoftware.com/products/writeroom">
         WrtRm
        </a>
        r
        <a href="http://www.ommwriter.com/">
         Ommwrtr
        </a>
        nd njy th fll-scrn fcsd glry, nd thn pst bck nt NV whn I’m dn, whr t’s nstntly svd. I lv nstnt sv — why sn’t ths dn lwys n vry prgrm?
       </li>
       <li>
        I hv  td lst n NV tht I dn’t rfr t vry ftn. I dn’t s td lsts mch nymr, xcpt s  dmpng grnd fr thngs I mght nd t rmmbr ltr. Mst dys I knw wht I wnt t wrk n — whtvr I’m xctd bt t th mmnt.
       </li>
       <li>
        Instd f kpng  lst f ds fr psts fr my blgs, I jst strt  nw pst (wth th prfx I mntnd bv). It’ll hv nts fr th pst. Thn whn I wnt t lk t my pst ds, I jst typ n th prfx (lk “zh” r “mnml”) nd I’ll s th lst f pst ds.
       </li>
       <li>
        I str thr snppts f txt, lk cmmnly sd html tgs I pt nt psts, r lnks t bk dwnlds fr ths wh hv trbl dwnldng, tc. On my ld Mc I hd ths snppts n
        <a href="http://smilesoftware.com/TextExpander/">
         TxtExpndr
        </a>
        , whch ws nc, bt I’v bn t lzy t st p TxtExpndr nd ll th snppts I s n my Mcbk Ar s thy’r n
        <span class="caps">
         NV.
        </span>
       </li>
      </ol>
      <p>
       Tht’s bt ll I cn thnk f. If y hv qstns, sk
       <a href="http://twitter.com/zen_habits">
        n Twttr
       </a>
       nd I’ll dd t ths pst.
      </p>
      <p>
       I lv NV fr ts lghtnss, ts smplcty, ts spd. It ds vrythng I nd wth  mnmm f fss, whch s bsclly prfct.
